window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>I always knew I was different; I just didn’t realize I belonged with the characters from horror movies.</b></p> <p>It turns out my abnormally accurate intuition is a bit more than that. I’m a psychic. And a witch. And the people that raised me? Not my biological parents.</p> <p>I would have loved a second to absorb this information, but the night I’m told the truth I get shipped off to a school for people like me...and shifters...and vampires (because they exist in real life, too).</p> <p><i>Drexel Academy is a slow-burn reverse-harem series.</i></p>"; 
